welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Raceland, where Southern hospitality meets small-town charm! Prepare to be enchanted by our scenic landscapes and rich history. We hope you have a wonderful stay and soak up all that our charming city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Terrebonne Airport serves all commercial flights and is equipped with modern amenities.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Terrebonne Airport caters to private and chartered flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
